                    cases: {
                        "@builtinTypes": "type",
                        "@default": "identifier"
                    }
                }
            ],
            // other built-ins
            [/\b([A-Z][a-zA-Z0-9]+\.[A-Z][a-zA-Z0-9]+)\b/,
                {
                    cases: {
                        "@builtinFunctions": "keyword.function",
                        "@builtinConstants": "constant",
                        "@default": "identifier"
                    }
                }
            ],
            // other identifiers
            [/\b([a-zA-Z_][\w\.]*)\b/, "identifier"],
            { include: "@whitespace" },
            { include: "@comments" },
            { include: "@strings" },
            [/[{}()\[\]]/, "@brackets"],
            [/([=\+<>\-\*&@\?\/!])|([<>]=)|(<>)|(=>)|(\.\.\.)|(\.\.)/, "operators"],
            [/[,;]/, "delimiter"],
        ],
        whitespace: [
            [/\s+/, "white"]
        ],
        comments: [
            ["\\/\\*", "comment", "@comment"],
            ["\\/\\/+.*", "comment"]
        ],
        comment: [
            ["\\*\\/", "comment", "@pop"],
            [".", "comment"]
        ],
        strings: [
            ["\"", "string", "@string"]
        ],
        string: [
            ["\"\"", "string.escape"],
            ["\"", "string", "@pop"],
            [".", "string"]
        ]
    }
};
